title: Boosted (In The Fast Lane) - Cole, Arya
description:
Coming up on her final year in law school Hannah is about
to make the biggest decision of her life: To follow the hopes
and dreams her parents had for her, or fuck it all and go her
own way with the most dangerous man she's ever met.

Brody's a bad boy, the complete opposite of Hannah, and he
couldn't have come at a better time than right in the middle of
her quarter-life crisis. He's a loner who lives his life on the other
side of the law, boosting cars for a crazy Russian mob boss, and
making more in five days driving than most people make all year.

His life is fast, it's dangerous, and it's full of deadly excitement -
just what Hannah has always wanted.Brody awakens uncontrollable
sexual urges in Hannah that she was too afraid to explore before,
but as she steps into his world she begins to open up in ways she
never imagined.

Will Hannah be able to survive in Brody's cut-throat
world of crime, sex, and living in the fast lane?



Boosted (In The Fast Lane #1)
By Arya Cole
Language: EN
Pages: PDF 463 - EPUB 263
